# PRODUCT CONTEXT — Grain v6

## What Grain Is

A steady alignment system.

A weekly reflection engine.

A trajectory integrity tool.

It protects long-term direction from short-term noise.

---

## What Grain Is Not

Not a:
- Task manager
- Habit tracker
- Streak app
- Time tracker
- Productivity optimizer
- Social platform
- Analytics dashboard

---

## Emotional Core

Users feel productive but unsure if it adds up.

Primary pain:
“I am doing a lot, but am I aligned?”

Grain surfaces that answer.

Not with judgment.
With reflection.

---

## Personality

Gentle guidance.
Not coaching intensity.
Not hype.

Clear.
Steady.
Honest.

---

## Constraints

- No gamification features.
- No streak mechanics.
- No public metrics.
- No comparison to other users.
- No optimization dashboards.
- No AI suggestions (MVP).

---

## Notification Philosophy

- No notification prompt during onboarding.
- Weekly email reminder (Sunday).
- Optional daily reminder (configurable).
- Browser push deferred.
- Earn attention before requesting permission.

---

## Core Loop

Declare.
Log.
Review.
Recalibrate.

Repeat weekly.

Alignment over intensity.